quran[7{c,v,t}:
24,21,"ae logo jo imaan laaye ho, shetan ke naqsh qadam par nah chalo is ki pairwi koi kere ga to woh usay fehash aur badi hi ka hukum day ga agar Allah ka fazl aur is ka reham o karam tum par nah hota to tum mein se koi shakhs pak nah ho sakta magar Allah hi jisay chahta hai pak kar deta hai, aur Allah suneney wala aur jan-nay wala hai"
24,22,"tum mein se jo log sahib fazl aur sahib mqdrt hain woh is baat ki qasam nah kha bathain ke apne rishta daar, maskeen aur mohajir fi Sabeel Allah logon ki madad nah karen ge inhen maaf kar dena chahiye aur dar guzar karna chahiye kya tum nahi chahtay ke Allah tumhe maaf kere? aur Allah ki sift yeh hai ke woh ghafoor aur Raheem hai"
24,23,"jo log pak daman, be khabar, momin aurton par tohmatain lagatay hain un par duniya aur akhirat mein laanat ki gayi aur un ke liye bara azaab hai"
24,24,woh is din ko bhool nah jayen jabkay un ki apni zubanain aur un ke apne haath paon un ke krtoton ki gawahi den ge
24,25,is din Allah woh badla inhen bharpoor day ga jis ke woh mustahiq hain aur inhen maloom ho jaye ga ke Allah hi haq hai sach ko sach kar dikhaane wala
24,26,"khabees aurtain khabees mardon ke liye hain aur khabees mard khabees aurton ke liye pakeeza aurtain pakeeza mardon ke liye hain aur pakeeza mard pakeeza aurton ke liye un ka daman pak hai unn baton se jo bananay walay banatay hain, un ke liye mughfirat hai aur rizaq kareem"
24,27,"ae logo jo imaan laaye ho, apne gharon ke siwa dosray gharon mein daakhil nah howa karo jab taq ke ghar walon ki Raza nah le lau aur ghar walon par salam nah bhaij lau, yeh tareeqa tumahray liye behtar hai tawaqqa hai ke tum is ka khayaal rakho ge"
